title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Sep 8 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Sep 8 2022
description:
C&B broadcast from KLBJ in Austin, Texas. Memphis murders crystalize America's #1 issue: crime. Memphis newscaster goes viral breaking down in tears over city's violence. Women in Memphis and all over America set up runs to honor Eliza Fletcher. Queen Elizabeth's health failing. Who knew Clay was a huge fan of the British royal family. Who would be a worse dinner guest for Clay and Buck? Jennifer Lawrence or Meghan Markle. Liberal Lawfare: New York DA Bragg indicts Bannon.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
